data.description:
18929 Southeast Hillcrest Drive in Tequesta, FL is ready for you! This solid CBS home is part of Jupiter Acres off County Line Road in Tequesta which offers a casual and relaxed lifestyle where you can feel the ocean breezes! The home is situated at the end of a quiet, well kept street on the Martin County side of Tequesta so you'll enjoy lower taxes.  With 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this 1032 square foot home sits on almost a 1/2 acre lot. There is an oversized garage and 2 attic accesses. The large back yard offers plenty of room to add your own pool and create the back yard oasis you've been dreaming about. The  shed has electricity and added storage - think a mans dream work bench or even a She Shed!The property also features a huge slab in the rear, ready for an addition should you choose to expand the current home. And the best part? No homeowners association, meaning you can truly live the good life without any restrictions.

Bike to the beach, Constitution Park, and all the quaint shops and restaurants that Tequesta has to offer. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this charming home your own!
